[02/06/2018 20:47:56] <font color="#00ff00">Francesca.</font>
[02/06/2018 20:47:58] <font color="#00ff00">¿Le acompaño?</font>
[02/06/2018 20:47:58] <font color="#ffff00">No, no. Ve a Narcóticos</font>
[02/06/2018 20:48:00] <font color="#ffff00">y pide información de Tallarita.</font>
[02/06/2018 20:48:02] <font color="#00ff00">Sí.</font>
